# Performance mods for Fabric 1.21.1

These mods directly improve modpack performance through code optimizations.


| Name | Links | Description | Alternatives |
|------|-------|-------------| --------------|
| Alternate Current | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/alternate-current) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/alternate-current) | Vanilla-compatible redstone optimizations | - |
| C2ME** | [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/c2me-fabric) | Allows chunkloading to be multithreaded, increasing worldgen speeds. Has frequent issues with mods that touch worldgen or threading | - |
| Connectivity | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/connectivity) | Fix Login timeouts, Packet sizes errors, Payloads errors, ghostblocks and more | [Packet Fixer](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/packet-fixer) |
| Dynamic FPS | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/dynamic-fps) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/dynamic-fps) | Improve performance when Minecraft is in the background | [FPS Reducer](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fps-reducer) |
| Fast Noise | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/zfastnoise) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/zfastnoise) | Optimizes worldgen speeds | - |
| Ferritecore* | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ferritecore) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/ferrite-core) | Memory usage optimizations | - |
| ImmediatelyFast | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/immediatelyfast) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/immediatelyfast) | Speed up immediate mode rendering in Minecraft | - |
| Ixeris | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ixeris) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/ixeris) | Buffered raw input and threaded event polling | - |
| ModernFix* | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/modernfix) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/modernfix) | All-in-one mod that improves performance, reduces memory usage, and fixes many bugs | - |
| Particle Core | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/particle-core) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/particle-core) | Particle optimizations | - |
| Quick Pack | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/quick-pack) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/quick-pack) | Improves datapack / resourcepack zip file loading times | - |
| ServerCore | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/servercore) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/servercore) | Various serverside optimizations. Breaks vanilla compatibility | - |
| Structure Essentials | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/structure-essentials-forge-fabric) | Performance improvements for structure searching | - |
| TerraBlenderFix** | [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/terrablenderfix) | Performance mod targeting [Terrablender](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/terrablender) surface rule injection methods. Reportedly breaks surface rule injections with certain Terrablender mods | - |

\* - A must-have mod for nearly any modpack. Only in very rare circumstances should you not use this mod or an equivalent.

** - Prone to issues or conflicts with other mods